# Typography Components

Use the shared Typography components from `@/components/ui/typography` for all text elements. Do not style headings, paragraphs, blockquotes, lists, or inline code with raw HTML plus Tailwind classes.

## Import

```tsx
import { Typography } from "@/components/ui/typography";
```

## Variant Mapping

| Use case | Component | Do not use |
|----------|-----------|------------|
| Page/section title | `Typography.H1` | `<h1 className="text-4xl font-bold">` |
| Section heading | `Typography.H2` | `<h2 className="text-3xl font-semibold">` |
| Subsection heading | `Typography.H3` | `<h3 className="text-2xl">` |
| Minor heading | `Typography.H4` | `<h4 className="text-xl">` |
| Body paragraph | `Typography.P` | `<p className="leading-7">` |
| Intro/lead text | `Typography.Lead` | `<p className="text-xl text-muted-foreground">` |
| Emphasized label | `Typography.Large` | `<div className="text-lg font-semibold">` |
| Small label/caption | `Typography.Small` | `<small className="text-sm">` |
| Muted helper text | `Typography.Muted` | `<p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground">` |
| Inline code | `Typography.Code` | `<code className="font-mono">` |
| Blockquote | `Typography.Blockquote` | `<blockquote className="border-l">` |
| Unordered list | `Typography.List` | `<ul className="list-disc">` |

## Usage

```tsx
// Good
<Typography.H1>Hello, Welcome to Kona Agency</Typography.H1>
<Typography.P className="text-muted-foreground">This is a test</Typography.P>
<Typography.Code>@radix-ui/react</Typography.Code>

// Bad
<h1 className="text-4xl font-bold">Hello</h1>
<p className="text-lg text-gray-600">This is a test</p>
<code className="font-mono">@radix-ui/react</code>
```

## Exceptions

- **Button/link text**: Use Button or Link components; their internal text styling is intentional.
- **Form labels**: Use Label component or Typography.Small for field labels.
- **Table cells**: Use Typography.TableHead / Typography.TableCell for table content, or raw `td`/`th` when table structure is custom.
- **Component library internals**: Do not change shadcn/ui or other third-party component source; their typography is part of the component API.

## Customization

Pass `className` to override or extend styles. Base styles are always applied first.

```tsx
<Typography.H1 className="text-center">Centered title</Typography.H1>
<Typography.P className="text-lg text-muted-foreground">Custom lead</Typography.P>
```
